            .col-md-5.col-sm-12

                .info(:class='{active: active === "whoami"}')
                    h2 Who am I?
                    p Born and raised in London UK, In 2009, I moved to Toronto, Canada and Colorado, USA in 2015.
                    p I balance my time behind the screen by staying active and healthy.
                    p Click an icon to explore my spare time.
                .info(:class='{active: active === "hockey"}')
                    h2 Ice Hockey
                    p I've been playing hockey for over 10 years.
                    p I've played in leagues, tournaments and recreational, but prefer now a relaxed pick-up.
                    p In winter I'll most likely be found playing on a pond under the stars.

                .info(:class='{active: active === "cooking"}')
                    h2 Cooking
                    p I'm passionate about cooking and good food; I rarely purchase products that have a nutrition label; I like to create everything from scratch using raw ingredients.
                    p I'll make my own bread, vinegar, butter, mayonnaise, flour, chili, pies etc.

                .info(:class='{active: active === "football"}')
                    h2 Football
                    p In 2010 I co-founded a flag football league in Toronto.
                    p While I no longer serve on the executive, the league is still going strong with 2 divisions, 14 teams and over 180 players providing an inclusive environment for people to learn and  football.

                .info(:class='{active: active === "offroad"}')
                    h2 Off Roading
                    p I'm excited to explore the offroad in an ATV, Jeep or dirtbike.
                    p Exploring the back trails is only a success if Jeep comes back covered in more mud than paint.

                .info(:class='{active: active === "food"}')
                    h2 Food and Agriculture
                    p I am very interested agriculture and mass food production industries.
                    p When sourcing my food I try to purchase from local farmers where I can be assure of animal welfare or no artificial ingredients.
                    p I grow my own non-GMO, non-hybrid, heritage strains of herbs, fruits and vegetables.

                .info(:class='{active: active === "county"}')
                    h2 Country
                    p I a big fan of country culture.
                    p I listen country music and somehow end up at every country concert or festival that comes to town.
                    p I enjoy summer evening under the stars, tailgates, fires or demolition derby.
